This page contains a '''list of kings''' (''mwami'', plural ''abami'') '''of [[Rwanda]]'''. The [[Kingdom of Rwanda]] was one of the oldest and the most centralized kingdoms in the history of [[Central Africa|Central]] and [[East Africa]].

Its state and affairs before King [[Gihanga]] is largely unconfirmed and highly shrouded in mythical tales.

